VDR Plugin 'skin flatPlus' Revision History
-------------------------------------------
2025-10-xx: Version 1.2.1
- [fix] Fix display of disk usage for menu category 0 (mcUndefined)
- [add] Clear font cache on plugin stop
- [add] Refactor GetIconName() function to cache all menu names and plugins,
        improving performance and reducing memory usage
- [add] Move GetFontAscender() to font cache
- [add] Setting for channel name and number font size in channel info
- [add] Setting to enable recording old file for old folder icon in recordings menu
- [add] Setting to enable audio format icon in channel info and recording info
- [update] Optimize justification of text
- [update] Use a minimum of 15 ms for scroll delay
- [update] Reduce number of calls to GetRecCounts() and UpdateTimerCounts()
- [update] Reduce number of calls to GetRecordingName() in SetItemRecording()
- [update] Remove any number of leading '%' from cutted recordings in menu
- [update] Refactor display menu to improve event and recording info handling
           with dedicated draw functions
- [update] Cache the value MaxX in TextScroller class to avoid repeated calculations
- [update] Use ShortText if Description is empty for event and recording information.
- [update] Use font cache for strings that seldom change
- [update] Calculate channel number width only when nessesary
- [update] Set margins relative to the OSD size
- [update] Set line width and line margin (Widgets, recording and event info)
           relative to the OSD size
- [update] Set margin for color buttons and message relative to the OSD size
- [update] Use a brighter 'Red' color for error marks
- [update] Use a brighter color for TopBarDateFont
- [update] Use a brighter color for format symbols like 4k or 1920x1080
- [update] Update script update_weather.sh to use '$LANG' if '$_LANG' is not set in *.conf
- [update] Remove obsolete 'pluginelper.h'
- [update] Calculate 'MenuPixmapViewPortHeight' only once in DrawMainMenuWidgets() function
- [update] Smaller VPS icon to save a little space
- [update] Reduce margin between actor images
- [update] Use signum 'Σ' prefix for length of recordings
- [update] In widget dvb devices show 'No DVB devices found' if no device is present
- [update] In widget last recordings show 'No recordings found' if no recording is present
- [update] Prefix timer with 'L:' for local and 'R:' for remote timers if no icon is
           available in timer widget
- [update] Same height for format icons hd.png, sd.png, crypted.png and uncrypted.png
- [update] Adjust color of unknown_res.png and unknown_format.png
- [update] Reduce size of shadow for vps.png
- [update] Some internal optimizations

